        History
        -------
        
        0.2.1 (2011-03-24)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * Python 2.5 Support
        * List of available colors
        
        
        0.2.0 (2011-03-23)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * Column Printing!!!
        * (Auto/Manual) Disabling of Colors
        * Smarter Colors
        * max_width, min_width
        * Strip cli colors
        * bug fixes
        
        
        0.1.2 (2011-03-21)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * Bugfixes
        
        
        0.1.1 (2011-03-20)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * Bugfixes
        * Indent Newline Injection
        * resources: flags, not_flags, files, not_files
        * Lots of Examples
        
        
        
        0.1.0 (2011-03-20)
        ++++++++++++++++++
        
        * Initial Release!
        
        
